data.description: Three bedroom, one bath home sitting on 1.39 acres with an inground pool waiting for your family. This home features new flooring, stainless appliances, granite countertops and newer cabinets. 3rd bedroom downstairs could be used as a family room. Pool is 'as is' and needs a new liner. Great location. 10 minutes to I-40 and 30 minutes to Turkey Creek in Knoxville.
